{"tid":1203102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術討論] 雷雨夜","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T11:40:34.000Z","uid":41389,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a17106a93582a5b61c2cb8a8cc98bc684b463337","tid":1203102,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"狗淋雨又重兵公園 我地可以轉攻其他位置 <br />\n如狗巢唱今天我 有幾大聲唱幾大聲 黑油加靚交通燈 用油洗下地板咁 晚上繼續集合物資 等等 <br />\n分散狗注意力 <br />\n如果狗忍唔住撒 就可以係深夜突襲 黎一個出奇不異 攻其不備<br />\n天公造美如果今夜落冰薄打爛佢d車更佳<br />\n<br />\n預計聽日狗都會重軍地鐵 請大家唔好帶任何「攻擊性武器」去到港島先補給 一係就深宵巴士<br />\n如果搭地鐵黎或者帶多套黑衣同口罩 但去到出左地鐵站先換 <br />\n盡量搭巴士 盡量搭巴士 盡量搭巴士 盡量搭巴士<br />\n<br />\n聽朝再一齊去番野餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c35c45f4f1bdf6fade254fa05865b7ff9076c74","tid":1203102,"uid":41389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:32:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有 如果聽朝唔衝但又想搭地鐵既市民 幫幫手著黑衣咩背囊 等狗唔好捉到義士</span></span>"},{"pid":"194420020db4311f730f963e25e5b05fe1a52d7f","tid":1203102,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66df7c587693eaad7f75d4dcb99b357be06d115","tid":1203102,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces